headline: What Analyst Projections for Key Metrics Reveal About Charles River (CRL) Q4 Earnings
summary: Besides Wall Street's top-and-bottom-line estimates for Charles River (CRL), review projections for some of its key metrics to gain a deeper understanding of how the company might have fared during the quarter ended December 2025.
